node.text:
@timberwolves All-Star @KarlTowns offers advice on how to get engaged in the movement for justice.

Tune in to @NBA Twitter & @TheNBPA Twitter at 4:00pm/et for A Conversation on Policing Reform – Presented by the National Basketball Social Justice Coalition

node.title: “If you see social injustice speak up.”
